scene.message:
Maki: Everyone's talking{nl}
about my mother, but...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
who do they mean?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I'd rather hold off on{nl}
seeing a doctor for a{nl}
while...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I wonder if Sonomura{nl}
still can't recall her mom.{nl}
Seems there's a story there.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Once we've healed up,{nl}
let's hurry to the abandoned{nl}
factory.{waitkey}But can we really get into{nl}
SEBEC from a place like that?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Get this — in that{nl}
last fight, I nearly got a{nl}
scar on my face!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ahh, I came this close{waitkey}to breaking the hearts of{nl}
500,000 Brown fans across{nl}
the land!{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, I'm so {wait_fr:21}care{wait_fr:16}-{wait_fr:16}less♥{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I won't get a shot,{nl}
right? Ayase really hates{nl}
shots...{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: An injured woman walked{nl}
by here a moment ago. I{nl}
wonder if a demon got her...{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Oh, hello. Your{nl}
friends are as full of{nl}
character as ever.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 800 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}
